---
// FounderMessage.astro
---

<main class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 dark:bg-gray-900 transition-colors duration-200">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 p-8 md:p-12 transition-colors duration-200">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
        For the Love of Compute
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg">
          <span class="text-5xl font-sans font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 float-left mr-3 -mt-1">W</span>
          elcome to ComputeSDK, where we're revolutionizing the way developers build high-performance computing applications. 
          What started as a simple idea has grown into a platform that empowers thousands of developers worldwide.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Our mission has always been clear: to simplify complex computing tasks without sacrificing power or flexibility. 
          Whether you're a startup building the next big thing or an enterprise scaling your infrastructure, 
          our tools are designed to help you focus on what matters most - creating exceptional software.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          At ComputeSDK, we believe that great technology should be accessible to everyone. That's why we've poured our 
          expertise into creating intuitive, powerful tools that abstract away the complexity while giving you the control you need.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          I'm incredibly proud of what our team has built, and I'm even more excited about what's to come. 
          Thank you for being part of our journey.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Garrison Snelling</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Founder, ComputeSDK</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="#get-started" class="px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-white bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 rounded-md shadow-sm transition-colors duration-200">
            Schedule a Demo
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 dark:text-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-300 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-md shadow-sm transition-colors duration-200">
            Contact Our Team
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
